`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Perm
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * perm <item> <affect> <level>

 Permanent flags are item flags such as haste, sneak, invisibility, fly,
detection, and so on.  If you wear an item with a perm flag it means that you
will have that flag on from that point on.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
